Build images:
docker build -t cluster_sensor_exporter ./simulated_nodes
docker build -t cluster_backup_service ./backup_service
docker build -t cluster_disk_health ./disk_health
docker build -t cluster_cluster_manager ./cluster_manager
docker build -t cluster_test_stress ./test_stress
docker build -t cluster_backup_service ./backup_service
docker build -t cluster_disk_health ./disk_health
docker build -t cluster_cluster_manager ./cluster_manager
docker build -t cluster_log_aggregator ./log_aggregator

Run containers:
docker stack deploy -c docker-stack.yml cluster

docker service logs cluster_test_stress



TO stop containers:
docker stack rm cluster


Unit Test
pytest -v filename